column2: SELECT a.ra, a.dec, psfFluxIvar_u, psfFluxIvar_g, psfFluxIvar_r, psfFluxIvar_i, psfFluxIvar_z, d.w1sigflux, d.w2sigflux, d.w3sigflux, d.w4sigflux INTO mydb.SFR_WISE_ERR FROM stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as a LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll as b on a.specObjID = b.specObjID LEFT JOIN WISE_xmatch as c on b.fluxObjID = c.sdss_objid LEFT JOIN WISE_allsky as d on c.wise_cntr = cntr LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll as p on b.fluxObjID = p.ObjID
